  "title": "History/Soc. Science SOL & Curriculum Framework; review of instruction on roles of all peoples.",
  "summary": "Commission on Civic Education; review; historically marginalized communities. Requires the Commission on Civic Education to review and make recommendations on the inclusion of the contributions, perspectives, and experiences of historically marginalized communities in the History and Social Science Standards of Learning and Curriculum Framework and any associated instructional guides and to include its findings and recommendations in its annual report.",
